<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n09002e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09002e">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09002e"> 2(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> I beg your pardon</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Mental Hospital / Coffin Placed Inside Asylum Grounds / &ldquo;A Disgraceful Act.&rdquo; &hellip; An Explanation</b> Night attendants Campbell and Hynes came before the meeting to explain why they had not reported an injury to a male patient in their division, who broke his leg &hellip; Dr. Mills said that those two particular attendants had since then absented themselves without leave, and he asked the committee for an order in the matter. / Attendant Hynes: <mark>I beg your pardon</mark> Dr. Mills. I was here in the hall from 12.30 till 4 o&apos;clock at the two previous meetings when this charge was discussed, expecting to be called in, and I went outside the gate on one occasion to send a wire concerning a daughter of mine who was seriously ill. That was the cause of the absence. <small> <a name="CT16feb24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CT16feb24"><cite title="source">Connacht Tribune</cite></a> (16 February 1924) 6/1</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c03051q" href="c03all.htm#c03051q">VI.C.03:051(q)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
